<hl style="text-align:center;">What is a Bibliography? </hl>
<p style="color:blue;"><1>A bibliography is a list of all of the resource you have used in the process of researching your work
<p style="color:blue;"><1>A list of the books and articles that have been used by someone when writing a particular book or article
<p style="color:blue;"><1>The main purpose of a bibliography entry is to give credit to authors whose work you have consulted in your research
<p style="text-align:center;"-"color:black;"> <b>In general, a bibliography should include the author's name, the titles of the works, the name and locations and others. </p>
